Fix the following java code

```java
class Ticket {
    final int MT = 1000;
    private int next = 0;

    public synchronized int getTicket() {
        next = next % MT + 1;
        return next;
    }
}

class Counter {
    final int MT = 1000;
    private int serve = 1;

    public synchronized void getCheese(int ticket) throws InterruptedException {
        while (ticket != serve) {
            wait();
        }
        serve = serve % MT + 1;
        notifyAll();
    }
}
```

解析H.264流和AAC流是一个相对复杂的过程，特别是在不使用ffmpeg库的情况下。然而，你可以选择使用其他开源库或者通过手动解析流中的NALU单元（H264）或ADTS帧（AAC）来实现。

对于H.264流，你可以使用开源库 x264（https://www.videolan.org/developers/x264.html）或OpenH264（https://github.com/cisco/openh264）。这些库提供了一系列用于解析H.264流的API。以下是使用x264库解析H.264流的简单示例：

```cpp
#include <x264.h>
#include <stdint.h>
#include <stdio.h>

void parse_h264_stream(const uint8_t *buffer, int length) {
    x264_nal_t *nal = NULL;
    int i_nal = 0;

    int result = x264_nal_decode(&nal, &i_nal, (uint8_t *)buffer, length);
    if (result < 0) {
        printf("Error decoding H.264 stream\n");
        return;
    }

    for (int i = 0; i < i_nal; i++) {
        x264_nal_t *current_nal = &nal[i];
        printf("NAL unit type: %d\n", current_nal->i_type);
    }

    x264_nal_release(nal);
}
```

对于AAC流，FAAD2（http://www.audiocoding.com/downloads.html）是一个用于解析AAC音频流的库。以下是使用FAAD库解析AAC流的简单示例：

```cpp
#include <neaacdec.h>
#include <stdint.h>
#include <stdio.h>

void parse_aac_stream(const uint8_t *buffer, int length) {
    NeAACDecHandle handle = NeAACDecOpen();

    NeAACDecConfigurationPtr conf = NeAACDecGetCurrentConfiguration(handle);
    conf->outputFormat = FAAD_FMT_16BIT; // output format, left as default
    NeAACDecSetConfiguration(handle, conf);

    long unsigned int sample_rate;
    unsigned char channels;
    int result = NeAACDecInit(handle, (uint8_t *)buffer, length, &sample_rate, &channels);
    if (result < 0) {
        printf("Error initializing AAC decoder\n");
        NeAACDecClose(handle);
        return;
    }

    NeAACDecFrameInfo frame_info;
    void *sample_buffer = NeAACDecDecode(handle, &frame_info, (uint8_t *)buffer, length);

    if (frame_info.error > 0) {
        printf("Error decoding frame: %s\n", NeAACDecGetErrorMessage(frame_info.error));
    } else {
        printf("AAC frame decoded successfully\n");
    }

    NeAACDecClose(handle);
}
```

请注意，这些示例假定你已经从输入流或文件中读取了原始的H.264或AAC数据。要手动解析这些格式，你需要了解H.264和AAC的详细规范，比如ISO/IEC 14496-10（H.264）和ISO/IEC 14496-3（AAC）。

